[div class=p 
	[em 
		"Super Bat Puncher
	]em
	" is a homebrew game for the NES by Morphcat, with music composed by Dave Harris. This TAS aims to complete two loops of the demo version of the game, using a bonus item that can only be obtained after the game has been completed once.
]div
